CustodyVerfcTypeOverride.name: CustodyVerfcTypeOverride
CustodyVerfcTypeOverride.description: Represents information about the verification of an entry in the chain of custody.

CountryId.description: The country for which the custody event is configured.

CustodyVerificationType.description: Specifies the type of verification required for a custody event.

DigitalVerificationSetupId.description: The digital verification setup associated with the override.

LastReferencedDate.description: The most recent date on which a user referenced the record.

LastViewedDate.description: The most recent date on which a user viewed the record.

Name.description: The name of the custody verification override record.

OwnerId.description: The owner of the custody verification override record.

Priority.description: The priority number assigned to the conditions that apply to the custody verification.

ServiceTerritoryId.description: The service territory for which custody is being configured.

TaskName.description: The task for which the custody event is being configured.

WorkProcedureId.description: The work procedure for which custody is being configured.

WorkTypeId.description: The work type for which custody is being configured.

WorkTypeStepId.description: The work type step for which custody is being configured.
